<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>J. Worden & Sons Asphalt Paving | Richmond's #1 Paving Legacy</title>
    <meta name="description" content="4th-generation J. Worden & Sons Asphalt Paving. Serving Richmond 23221, Chester, and 41 cities since 1984. Driveways, parking lots, and sealcoating.">
